===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Brycen (Masters)}}
Brycen forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Cryogonal}} and {{p|Walrein}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. As Brycen-Man, Brycen forms a sync pair with {{p|Zoroark}}. Brycen became a playable sync pair since the game's release, with him appearing as Brycen-Man on April 30, 2024.

